OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780484573
OL,3,CForeign Secretary says Mandelson
OL,4,Cshould 'never have been appointed'
OL,6,FLord Peter Mandelson should "never
OL,7,Fhave been appointed" as ambassador to
OL,8,Fthe US, Yvette Cooper has said.
OL,10,FMore than a thousand files were
OL,11,Freleased by the government on Monday
OL,12,Fafter MPs forced it to share all the
OL,13,Fdocuments it had on Mandelson's
OL,14,Fappointment as US ambassador.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
