PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780484573
OL,3,CForeign Secretary says Mandelson
OL,4,Cshould 'never have been appointed'
OL,6,FThe documents featured numerous
OL,7,Fmessages between Mandelson and several
OL,8,Fministers, including records of
OL,9,FWhatsApp exchanges between Lord
OL,10,FMandelson and Cabinet minister Pat
OL,11,FMcFadden, where the minister expressed
OL,12,Ffrustration with his party colleagues.
OL,14,FHe complained that Labour MPs were
OL,15,F"asking the wrong questions" and that
OL,16,F"every meeting I have is 'who can we
OL,17,Ftax in order to pay benefits to
OL,18,Fothers'".
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@\O]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
